{
  "stem": "1828.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she came-- they came back, those three, and they said-- my sister said, on the bottom of the stones is a package for you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was, again, my contacts that knew we--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were able to find--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--they didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was mis-delivered to these people who-- who were wondering whether it was one of us, because, first of all, it was a girl's name.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Secondly, it wasn't-- they were French there, and so in came this packaging, and there was flour in it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all that was left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Obviously, there had been a lot more in it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a letter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a letter that they-- that they got indirect knowledge of us and that we're together, and that we should keep our-- our spirits up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the war is going to be over soon and all that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother took that flour and mixed it with water and made [NON-ENGLISH] out of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Miraculous, and the whole room where we were staying together partook of that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was like a party.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It wasn't filling or anything, but everyone that was a-- from outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was another experience we had there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had become-- we knew each other very well by that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were only about 20 people in that one room, all women that had started out together, many of them from Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we-- we knew each other well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We helped each other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We warned each other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was-- it had crystallized into a good group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And somehow, one or two people from outside, they had no room in the other room, so they brought them to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was a problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Bread was disappearing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the rations, things were missing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I saw justice administered.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
